                  </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THIRD COURT</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">Tuesday, August</hi> 24<hi rend="italic">th</hi>, 1847.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">PRESENT</hi>—Sir <hi rend="smallCaps">CHAPMAN MARSHALL</hi>, Knt., Alderman; Mr. Alderman <hi rend="smallCaps">WOOD</hi>; and <hi rend="smallCaps">EDWARD BULLOCK</hi>, Esq.</p>
